        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 2. Maximum likelihood (ML) tree of a 458 bp sequence of mitochondrial 16S rRNA for samples of Leptobrachella (for sample details, see Table 1). Numbers above nodes represent the support values (BS/BPP). Newly obtained sequences are shown by bold face. Asterisks indicate the nodes with sufficient support (BS ≥ 70% and BPP ≥ 0.95)." ;
